This is my solution to Exercise 4

This can be found at https://github.com/BenjaminLiuPenrose/PyAssignmentSolution

First, go to 4.1_Solution, 
for exercise 4.1.1 to 4.1.4, run 4.1_Main.py, follow the instrcutions in shell step by step
for exercise 4.1_Main.py, follow the instrcutions in shell step by step
implementation code for this part can be found at 4.1_Solution\Implementations\Timer.py

Second, go to 4.2_Solution, 
for exercise 4.2.1 to 4.2.4 run 4.2_Main.py in shell, follow the instrcutions in shell step by step
implementation code for this part can be found at 4.2_Solution\Implementations\Timer.py, Loan.py

Third, go to 4.3_Solution, 
for exercise 4.3.1 to 4.3.8 run 4.3_Main.py in shell, follow the instrcutions in shell step by step
implementation code for this part is followed by the main() function


